Version 0.1.2 (2026-05-29)
* Subcommand framework with eight commands: search, install, remove,
  rebuild, list, update, register, unregister (all are stubs).
* Internationalization: gettext support with Chinese (zh_CN) translation.
* Utility module with classic fork+exec helper for subprocess execution.
* Command-line argument parsing and dispatch via table-driven lookup.
* po/ directory with translation infrastructure (POT, PO, LINGUAS).
Version 0.1.1 (2026-05-26)
* Build system: add GitHub Actions CI with automatic distcheck and release.
Version 0.1.0 (2026-05-26)
* Initial project skeleton with autotools build system.
* Basic hello world program for testing.
* Trivial test suite with make check.
